               <msContents>
                  <summary>Teaching of Christ, ትምህርተ፡ ክርስቶስ፡, a Catholic Catechism, edited by Roberto Bellarmino (Rome, 1736) in Ge’ez, Italian, and Arabic in parallel columns.</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1"><locus from="2r" to="53v" facs="002">Fols 2r–53v</locus><title>Teaching of Christ, <foreign xml:lang="gez">ትምህርተ፡ክርስቶስ፡</foreign></title>
                 <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz, Italian, Arabic, Hebrew</textLang>
                 <note>Dottrina Cristiana Compossta dall’Emo, e Rmo Cardinale Roberto Bellarmino, a Catholic Catechism, edited by Roberto Bellarmino (Rome, 1736) in Ge’ez, Italian, and Arabic in parallel columns. On <locus target="#48v #49r #49v">fols. 48v, 49r, 49v</locus>, there is a chart showing the parallel Hebrew and Ethiopic alphabet equivalents.</note>
               </msItem>
               </msContents>
